7-13T16:40:24.000Z","msg":"樓主我都係做呢行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n細公司，生意唔多<br />\nproject 無錢分<br />\n有無好介紹"},{"pid":"438d190afd2a05d5e5d8a7761d5be362ce1302d3","tid":320554,"uid":119864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T16:40:27.000Z","msg":"應該係醒目仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b09eb840678302bc36938e25dfedfa3e92102c6","tid":320554,"uid":111088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T16:40:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>做廣告<br />\n供車<br />\n養車 無撚左一皮<br />\n家用6~7 千 睇心情<br />\n必要洗費 最多皮半 (買衫養女娛樂）<br />\n保險 2 千<br />\n廢唔廢？<br />\n身邊even 係做寬頻既都儲得多過我。。。</blockquote><br />\n冇人叫你想儲錢都學人去玩車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實有公司車 但係我撚想揸七人車<br />\n一d 霸氣都無<br />\n利申 揸緊垃圾Z4</blockquote><br />\n其實有冇考慮過唔好揸車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b3eefe39414fafdeb4489253a64a922aa3e2499","tid":320554,"uid":100965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T16:40:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>冇錢就咪撚玩車 買咁重保險啦<br />\n依家你曬命定串人 <br />\nBTW 廢</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n樓主得中六學歷<br />\n係佢同學當中可能係算高人工果堆<br />\n但其實係香港<br />\n3xk有乜柒意義？"},{"pid":"b78a60c15e7a3f3d36bd4b57462e7dcb59405469","tid":320554,"uid":54946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T16:46:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>做廣告可以點入行  成日都覺日本個啲無厘頭廣告好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申 乞食科</blockquote><br />\n我講出黎一定比人話母幹<br />\n我舅父係呢行無人唔識<br />\n開頭佢帶我入行 扣埋老強得萬二蚊人工架咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實香港黎講呢行好細，來來去去個班人<br />\n呢行最講係人脈 第二係運氣 第三先係實力<br />\n讀完乜乜物物出到黎其實無撚用<br />\n當你傻仔boy 咁洗架咋<br />\n入行認真唔難 捱到一年先係最難</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n日日ot 有大project個陣唔識訓都幾辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /