yTime":"2017-07-13T17:02:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主我都係做呢行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n細公司，生意唔多<br />\nproject 無錢分<br />\n有無好介紹</blockquote><br />\n行內出名，搵到錢都係個十間八間間 <br />\n除左Axxx Cxxx之外其他都無伏 可以試下搭路入<br />\n入去做要有planning ,唔識人唔緊要<br />\n唔識做人就最濕滯"},{"pid":"2124228edf0c30849bd519d223333009018297ee","tid":320554,"uid":51269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T17:04:07.000Z","msg":"唔撚養車咪儲多啲錢囉 又要養車又要玩 之後仲問人廢唔廢,答你廢就會存多啲架咩"},{"pid":"969417548a0b1d9f26f8ff6bb8d28342fd7a325d","tid":320554,"uid":32631,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T17:06:12.000Z","msg":"其實晒命post 者唔洗咁認真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nbtw 廢， 我而家30歲60k 25果時已經買左樓，28歲先有一架車，太早學人養車係幼稚"},{"pid":"1e329c2b1dc5d8116a20571bfb67fbb16271984c","tid":320554,"uid":46595,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T17:07:28.000Z","msg":"請善用起底功能<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efb471e2c8beb5c267588a2ce60088ac2c0463a7","tid":320554,"uid":59649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T17:12:34.000Z","msg":"廢<br />\n廿中50k 養車 家用 包條女<br />\n月儲3xk"},{"pid":"cfeb102f750efd8c82bd1bb0d09ccfb15d8a2d37","tid":320554,"uid":96574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T17:13:19.000Z","msg":"其他堅做廣告既巴打問既問題 一律唔回應 好野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f24be0514d04cc0b24bc238e425c034662a0805e","tid":320554,"uid":30508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T17:15:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>做廣告可以點入行  成日都覺日本個啲無厘頭廣告好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申 乞食科</blockquote><br />\n我講出黎一定比人話母幹<br />\n我舅父係呢行無人唔識<br />\n開頭佢帶我入行 扣埋老強得萬二蚊人工架咋<